Set 1

Shakedown Street, New Minglewood Blues, Friend Of The Devil, Hell In A Bucket , Bird Song, It's All Over Now, Might As Well

U.S. Blues

Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums

reviews.review_text:
Finally Thank you for still being so active in our community. Your tour notes are exactly same scene myself and my touring friends were part of.  Brings back a lot of great Grate memory's coming flooding back . The whole ticket stub story is like it were yesterday. I wonder if we crossed paths back then ?  We did the hot springs many times.
 Your quality is so much better then what we have had on the archives for years. I for one thank you .  The sound here is close to a 5 star sound if not for the cut in Shakedown it would be 5 stars. Not that missing a bit of it matters now so with that said I am giving it a 5 star rating because it's like running into that old girlfriend that you always loved even though you broke up years ago.
